So, YouTube doesn't allow my ad blockers to work anymore. So, I made my own ad blocker, sort of. Now, when an ad comes up, within 3 seconds, it will reload the page. If another ad shows up after that, within 3 seconds, it reloads the page until the video comes up. Not perfect but it works!
Am I missing something, or did the Google AI fail twice? I mean, I know it isn't hard to believe it did, but I wanna make sure I'm not having a stroke.
